Author: baronofficiall2
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Today there are more than one problem in the decentralized manufacturing market, which leads to bottlenecks in manufacturing. In particular, inefficiency, costly resource use, minimum order quantity, inappropriate registration, lack of follow-up, lack of IP defense, logistical time and price, and ecological pressure are sources of these problems. Here, Productivist, the first peer-to-peer network that brings together customers and specialized and skilled producers has emerged, mapping global manufacturing capacities to account for solving all these problems. The Productivist block-chain project aims to create an open data stream that will allow private individuals and companies to power the industrial revolution at 4.0 on a random scale. The only solution available at the point where the production world has come in recent times is seen as heavy investments, deportation and aggressive administration. The Productivist approach is to offer a clear, free and global alternative through technology. Because of the tremendous potential of block-chain technology that has been discovered since 2008 and has become increasingly obvious, and because of the quality of the services it provides, each sector has begun to explore the opportunity to contribute to the management of its dataflow. The Productivist approach also seeks to use the great power that this new generation of technology can offer to its production life in general. Productivist looked at Freelabster.com in 2016, creating a common network connecting three-dimensional printing professionals to potential customers. This very strong network grew rapidly in the last 2 years and continued to grow day by day. Today there are over 3,000 certified Freelabsters serving both the private sector and the public sector. With this experience, the Productivist approach will not only open the Freelabster concept to all production technologies, but will also provide access to a global production capacity map, providing security and confidentiality through the Smart Contract Protocol. In the wake of all this formation, the Block Chain and Productivist project will provide a transparent solution to keep records in followers, feedback to customers, along with their indices in real time, as well as being a standard for the new era of intelligent production. Open chains are open to customers and producers. and will be free of charge, the Productivist Standard will be used for these transactions. Hyperlink technology will also be used to provide the best experience for customers and manufacturers who use block chains in the Productivist approach. Within this project, intelligent instruments will be notified in real time about which machine is ready for use during production, real time viewing, usage optimization and scaling will be done to increase production capacity and productivity. The quality, transparency and authenticity will be guaranteed by the system thanks to the pre-production and post-production on the blockchain. Optimized production with a balanced and secure network will ensure that each supplier will receive equal and customized order shipments. Thanks to Blockchain technology, the security of your important models will always be at the top.  The Productivist project will contribute significantly to the manufacturing sector. We can list these benefits in the following way;  Efficiency in all processes, - Welding use, -Minimum order quantity not to have, -If there is a recordable record, -Providing real time progress, Providing full IP defense -It will be produced in the region, -Low shipping is to offer better production.  Benefits for producers: Optimized production, Time and cost efficiency, Transactional security, New opportunities, Decentralization, Environmentally friendly production.  The advantages for customers are; Ease of use of resources, Affordable prices, Transparency, Security, Expert Network and Monitoring.

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Hey bitminerox0621, thanks for your post.  Productivist is using the blockchain to offer a fully automated production process.  Supply chain management can get easier with the 2 modes that can be used by manufacturers with the smart device Productivist is developing : “commercial mode” on: when it is activated, it will be possible to send production instructions directly to the machine and fill production time voids without any other intervention "commercial mode" off: will still allow to remotely monitor the production schedule More info about the commercial mode can be found pages in our white paper ( https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oksLkRIWWF03NJzxPX_EUbC22041hjhk/ ) > 3.2 A device to connect them all (pages 16 & 17)   And do we have continuous improvement plan on each process or production lines?  An element that can help improving production lines is the Scoring System that Productivist has designed. This is a score calculated after checking manufacturers’ material, location, experience, availability, and manufacturing capacity. This will help to allocate the production to the best manufacturer (depending on each client's need) and will be an info that can be used to understand what needs to be improved in order to optimize production.  More info about the Scoring System on these 2 articles we published on Medium : Productivist’s Scoring System: It’s a match ! > https://medium.com/productivist/productivist-scoring-system-its-a-match-4b2ba3f8c9a0 A detailed insight of the Productivist Scoring System > https://medium.com/productivist/a-detailed-insight-of-the-productivist-scoring-system-7dea1ceb8d53  We hope these elements are helping you. Feel free to ask any further question below or directly on our telegram group : https://t.me/productivist

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Hello, community!  The pre-ICO is about to begin and all the team is really excited about it! We are sure that all the positive feedback we are receiving for weeks will help us reach our goals.  In case you missed it, I am posting this reminder to give you all the info you need to be among the first to invest in the Productivist Blockchain Project by purchasing ProducTokens :  The pre-ICO phase is starting the 1st of May 2018 and will end the 15th of May 1 PROD = 0.1€ = 0.12$ 28% BONUS will be applied to ALL investments in the Productivist Blockchain Project during this phase. You can purchase ProducTokens using Ethereum, Bitcoin, Litecoin, Dogecoin, Dash, FIAT - SEPA transfer (minimum 10k€) PROD tokens can be purchased through any ERC-20 compliant wallet  This first phase will be followed by others during which bonuses will never be as high as in the pre-ICO. In other words, investing during the pre-ICO is the best way to maximize the number of PROD you will get.  Keep in mind that by investing in the Productivist Blockchain Project, you are investing on a project that aims at getting a first role in the industrial revolution 4.0. This new era needs standards to lead to a whole new way of production that: - Correct inefficiency - Increase intellectual property protection - Improve trust between parts involved - Help production tracking  Our final goal is to become that standard, and this is why we need you.  You will find all details about how Productivist can help production go to the next level by :  - Checking our whitepaper: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oksLkRIWWF03NJzxPX_EUbC22041hjhk/view - Talking directly with the team on telegram: https://t.me/productivist - Visiting our website: https://ico.productivist.com/ - Reading our articles on Medium: medium.com/productivist   Let's make it happen!

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Hi Gulinborsti, The team behind Productivist is the same team which founded Freelabster.com a few years ago. This has been an enormous success and is now one of the biggest 3D printing platforms on the market. Right after the ICO, you will be able to use your PROD to purchase 3D printing on the Freelabster.com platform.  Since Productivist protocol is open and flexible we invite all the marketplaces and internal services to join the community and empower the Productivist revolution.  Freelabster.com will be the first marketplace to join the Productivist protocol.  Productivist will provide blockchain access, APIs, and SDKs to anyone who wants to open a decentralized production service. Instantly connecting them directly to thousands of smart manufacturers of any kind.  Cheers,

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Thank you Daniel.  The Productivist eco-system,including its blockchain, intends to become the standard of the new smart manufacturing era. It will provide a transparent solution to track records, store client feedback and index in real time all the manufacturer’s information.  You can find all the details and the other applications on the blockchain in this document : https://drive.google.com/open?id=1KuSufU-slgXWVLHV5rPPvLSGUppUxaGa And we published on github our initial work and the coding of the 4 main apps running on the blockchain : https://github.com/Productivist/productivist-yp/blob/master/productivist-blockchain.md  A major advantage will be the fact that the blockchain will be open and free for all clients and manufacturers.  All the servers and transaction fees will be paid for by the marketplaces and services using the Productivist Protocol.  All this will be backed by the use of Hyperledger technology meeting needs of the manufacturing industry and will ensure a seamless experience for everyone using the Productivist protocol.

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Our Hardcap is 50 million Euros equals to 65% of the token sale considering the bonus. Our Softcap is 3 million. If we don't meet the softcap we refund the investors.  For your info :  SOFT CAP : 3,000,000 € This first cap will allow the creation of the Productivist Blockchain Project with the majority of funds being invested in infrastructure and software development.  MID CAP : 20,000,000 € This second cap will lead us to a much efficient creation of the Productivist service. The Productivist Solution would be fully integrated to Freelabster website and associated services. The R&D for the smart devices would start right after the end of the ICO.  HARD CAP : 50,000,000 € This last cap will allow us to accelerate the mass production of the smart device that will connect machines to the blockchain and enable access to all verticals. In this way, the roadmap can be significantly shortened and the development more efficient by hiring a bigger dev team.

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: Thank you for the opportunity to describe more the project :  First of all, this is the first peer-to-peer network connecting private and professional manufacturers to their clients by mapping global manufacturing capacities.  We want to tackle the bottleneck between clients and manufacturers by decentralizing the global ecosystem and give them direct access to each other. By the way... We are from Freelabster, one of the biggest 3D printing marketplace in Europe.   The blockchain and the Productivist project will become a standard of the new smart manufacturing era. Basically, it will be a transparent solution to track records, store clients feedbacks and index in real time all the manufacturers. The blockchain will be open and free for the clients and the manufacturers. All servers fee paid by the marketplaces and services using the Productivist Standard. We are using the Hyperledger technology to ensure the best experience for the clients and manufacturers using the blockchain.  The smart device will tell in real time which machine is ready to be used. Real time monitoring, usage optimisation and scaling.  The services using the blockchain We invite all marketplaces and internal services to join the community and empower the Productivist revolution. A blockchain access, APIs and SDKs will be provided to anyone who wants to open a decentralized production service. They will be directly connected to thousand of smart manufacturers of any kind.  The PROD The PROD is the currency of the Productivist blockchain, it will run on Ethereum blockchain to ensure the best compatibility with exchanges and to keep the cash on a public BC. Any services will be ordered in PROD tokens. When a customer wants to purchase a manufacturing service, he will be able to use €,$ or any traditional currency. The fiat will be changed to PROD (in the background), organized and managed by a third party.  The Productivist reserve will be held by a foundation that will ensure the stability of the rate during an order. For example, if you purchase a production when the PROD is equal to 1€ and 3 weeks later the PROD equals 0,95€, the compensation management will ensure that the manufacturer will get paid the right amount he quoted.  At the end of the order, the manufacturer will be incentivized to keep and use his PROD to purchase material and machinery. Manufacturers will also be able to change their tokens into FIAT thanks to a third party change bureau.  The compensation management is exclusively here to ensure the manufacturer will be paid the right amount. However, it will not stop the coin to rise in value. Any time a partner is joining the ecosystem they will be asked to purchase a significant amount of tokens. The coin will also rise accordingly to the business performance of the entire ecosystem.    Join us and be part of the smart manufacturing revolution.

Author: productivist
Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: FAQ  What is the Productivist's project? The first peer-to-peer network connecting private and professional manufacturers to their clients by mapping global manufacturing capacities.  Do you have a hard cap? Our hard cap is 65 million (65%) PROD tokens or 50 million € for the ICO participants.  What cryptocurrencies do you accept to receive ProducTokens? We accept BTC, ETH, LTC, DASH and DOGE.  Will PROD tokens be ERC20 token? Yes.  When the PRE-ICO and ICO going to start? The dates will be announced soon. Join our Telegram group to be the first to know.  Are there any bonuses? Yes. Check the timeline to find the %.  Where can I see the smart contract? You will find our smart contract on our Github.  Can I send crypto from exchanges? Yes you can. You can send cryptos from Coinbase, Bittrex, Binance...  How will I receive my PROD tokens? During your KYC process, you will be asked to provide your Ethereum address to receive your tokens.  Do you have a KYC? During the potential account verification (KYC) we may require a proof of ID and proof of address. Citizens or residents of the United States (or any other jurisdictions, where participation in the Productivist token distribution event is or may be considered unlawful or illegal) are not allowed to participate.  When will I receive my PROD tokens? Tokens will be delivered with smart contract shortly after the ICO ends.  Where can I get help or find out more info? You can join our Telegram group.  How can I participate in the the ICO? Just signup to ico.productivist.com/tokensale and follow the steps.  On what exchanges PROD tokens would be listed? At this point we are unfortunately not able to reveal information regarding exchanges. It will be published after our ICO. Be aware that a Productivist’s employee will have the full-time mission to promote the ProducToken and list the coin into majors Exchanges.  What is the minimum and maximum participation stake? 1 PROD (0,1€).  Do you have referral system? Yes we have. Signup on ico.productivist.com/tokensale to get you referral link. More informations in the Bounty & Referral PDF document.  Is there a bounty program? Yes we have. Signup on ico.productivist.com/tokensale to apply to Bounties. More informations in the Bounty & Referral PDF document.

Title: [ANN][ICO]🔥🚀 PRODUCTIVIST - Smart-Manufacturing empowered by the Blockchain
Body: 4.0 is referred to as the fourth industrial revolution. Industry 4.0 creates a "smart factory" due to cyber-physical systems, Internet of things, cloud and cognitive computing. The Productivist blockchain project, in particular, aims to create not only an open data stream, giving access to private individuals and companies of any scale a global map of manufacturing capacities, but it will also provide security and privacy through Smart Contract Protocol. Our goal is to create a new standard while maintaining at all times a guarantee of quality, fair pricing and efficiency.
